Shanghai GDP up 13 . 7 percent in first half . Shanghai ' s gross domestic product ( GDP ) rose by a year - on - year 13 . 7 percent to 154 . 363 billion yuan in the first half of this year , the Business News said on Tuesday . At a meeting on Monday , mayor Xu Kuangdi asked government departments to make further efforts in the second half to ensure the city ' s GDP growth for the full year topped 10 percent , the newspaper said . It gave no further details . ( $ 1 = 8 . 3 yuan ) 
